#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an3.124"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.124:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.124:0.2"
msgid "13. Kusināravagga "
msgstr "13. Kusināra "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.124:0.3"
msgid "124. Bhaṇḍanasutta "
msgstr "124. Arguments "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an3.124:1.1"
msgid "“Yassaṃ, bhikkhave, disāyaṃ bhikkhū bhaṇḍanajātā kalahajātā vivādāpannā aññamaññaṃ mukhasattīhi vitudantā viharanti, manasi kātumpi me esā, bhikkhave, disā na phāsu hoti, pageva gantuṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I’m not even comfortable thinking about a place where mendicants argue—quarreling and fighting, continually wounding each other with barbed words—let alone going there. "

msgctxt "an3.124:1.2"
msgid "Niṭṭhamettha gacchāmi: "
msgstr "I come to a conclusion about them: "

#. VAR: bahulamakaṃsu → bahulīmakaṃsu (s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "an3.124:1.3"
msgid "‘addhā te āyasmanto tayo dhamme pajahiṃsu, tayo dhamme bahulamakaṃsu. "
msgstr "‘Clearly those venerables have given up three things and cultivated three things.’ "

msgctxt "an3.124:1.4"
msgid "Katame tayo dhamme pajahiṃsu? "
msgstr "What three things have they given up? "

msgctxt "an3.124:1.5"
msgid "Nekkhammavitakkaṃ, abyāpādavitakkaṃ, avihiṃsāvitakkaṃ—"
msgstr "Thoughts of renunciation, good will, and harmlessness. "

msgctxt "an3.124:1.6"
msgid "ime tayo dhamme pajahiṃsu. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an3.124:1.7"
msgid "Katame tayo dhamme bahulamakaṃsu? "
msgstr "What three things have they cultivated? "

msgctxt "an3.124:1.8"
msgid "Kāmavitakkaṃ, byāpādavitakkaṃ, vihiṃsāvitakkaṃ—"
msgstr "Sensual, malicious, and cruel thoughts. … "

msgctxt "an3.124:1.9"
msgid "ime tayo dhamme bahulamakaṃsu’. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an3.124:1.10"
msgid "Yassaṃ, bhikkhave, disāyaṃ bhikkhū bhaṇḍanajātā kalahajātā vivādāpannā aññamaññaṃ mukhasattīhi vitudantā viharanti, manasi kātumpi me esā, bhikkhave, disā na phāsu hoti, pageva gantuṃ. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an3.124:1.11"
msgid "Niṭṭhamettha gacchāmi: "
msgstr "I come to a conclusion about them: "

msgctxt "an3.124:1.12"
msgid "‘addhā te āyasmanto ime tayo dhamme pajahiṃsu, ime tayo dhamme bahulamakaṃsu’. "
msgstr "‘Clearly those venerables have given up three things and cultivated three things.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli1.276, sc2
msgctxt "an3.124:2.1"
msgid "Yassaṃ pana, bhikkhave, disāyaṃ bhikkhū samaggā sammodamānā avivadamānā khīrodakībhūtā aññamaññaṃ piyacakkhūhi sampassantā viharanti, gantumpi me esā, bhikkhave, disā phāsu hoti, pageva manasi kātuṃ. "
msgstr "I feel comfortable going to a place where the mendicants live in harmony—appreciating each other, without quarreling, blending like milk and water, and regarding each other with kindly eyes—let alone thinking about it. "

msgctxt "an3.124:2.2"
msgid "Niṭṭhamettha gacchāmi: "
msgstr "I come to a conclusion about them: "

msgctxt "an3.124:2.3"
msgid "‘addhā te āyasmanto tayo dhamme pajahiṃsu, tayo dhamme bahulamakaṃsu. "
msgstr "‘Clearly those venerables have given up three things and cultivated three things.’ "

msgctxt "an3.124:2.4"
msgid "Katame tayo dhamme pajahiṃsu? "
msgstr "What three things have they given up? "

msgctxt "an3.124:2.5"
msgid "Kāmavitakkaṃ, byāpādavitakkaṃ, vihiṃsāvitakkaṃ—"
msgstr "Sensual, malicious, and cruel thoughts. "

msgctxt "an3.124:2.6"
msgid "ime tayo dhamme pajahiṃsu. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an3.124:2.7"
msgid "Katame tayo dhamme bahulamakaṃsu? "
msgstr "What three things have they cultivated? "

msgctxt "an3.124:2.8"
msgid "Nekkhammavitakkaṃ, abyāpādavitakkaṃ, avihiṃsāvitakkaṃ—"
msgstr "Thoughts of renunciation, good will, and harmlessness. … "

msgctxt "an3.124:2.9"
msgid "ime tayo dhamme bahulamakaṃsu’. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an3.124:2.10"
msgid "Yassaṃ, bhikkhave, disāyaṃ bhikkhū samaggā sammodamānā avivadamānā khīrodakībhūtā aññamaññaṃ piyacakkhūhi sampassantā viharanti, gantumpi me esā, bhikkhave, disā phāsu hoti, pageva manasi kātuṃ. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an3.124:2.11"
msgid "Niṭṭhamettha gacchāmi: "
msgstr "I come to a conclusion about them: "

msgctxt "an3.124:2.12"
msgid "‘addhā te āyasmanto ime tayo dhamme pajahiṃsu, ime tayo dhamme bahulamakaṃsū’”ti. "
msgstr "‘Clearly those venerables have given up three things and cultivated three things.’” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.124:2.13"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

